com.onfleet.demo.homework.util

Class SampleDataset

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onfleet.demo.homework.util.SampleDataset
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @Immutable
public final class SampleDataset
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a generated (or loaded) sample dataset, comprised of Location, Driver, and Task records. This dataset structure is used before tasks are assigned.
